title: An Act relative to the Massachusetts Poland Trade Commission

abstracts.abstract: By Representative Kushmerek of Fitchburg, a petition (accompanied by bill, House, No. 3376) of Michael P. Kushmerek and Jacob R. Oliveira for legislation to establish a commission on Massachusetts-Poland trade within the International Trade Office.  State Administration and Regulatory Oversight.
